            button.tablink.w3-bar-item.w3-button(onclick="openBook(event, 'booksCheckedOut')") Books - Checked Out
            button.tablink.w3-bar-item.w3-button(onclick="openBook(event, 'booksOverdue')") Books - Overdue
        #books-all.w3-container.book
